{"tid":335163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［死撚左佢啦］在西九站月台可否上FB？袁國強：好問題，我也想知道答案","createTime":"2017-07-25T11:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T01:37:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"663baf240fd7e9d2057c2cf33300d3032cb00bd0","tid":335163,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"政府今日公佈高鐵西九龍站「一地兩檢」方案，高鐵站地下第二至四層共10.5萬平方米的「內地口岸區」以及高鐵列車車廂範圍內，適用內地法律，由內地法院行使司法管轄權，僅六項民事相關事項仍受香港法律管轄。被問到如有人在西九站內地口岸區內示威、喊六四口號或打交會如何處理，袁國強稱旅客一旦進入「其他管轄區的檢疫範圍」就要遵守當地法律。至於如有人在口岸區內打架送到香港醫院，保安局局長李家超指，會當作未辦入境手續處理，不適合入境者會送離香港範圍。<br />\n<br />\n至於在西九站內地口岸區內的內地執法人員會否配槍，李家超則稱由內地當局決定。<br />\n<br />\n下為記者會部份問題節錄：<br />\n<br />\n問：如果有人在內地口岸區示威、嗌六四口號，或打交犯法，執法情況如何？如果在高鐵列車上違反內地法律，但離開了車廂踏上路軌（屬香港境內），如何處理？<br />\n<br />\n袁國強：當旅客進入其他管轄區的檢疫範圍，都要守當地法律&hellip;一地兩檢不過是將兩個口岸拉埋一齊啫，法律上的權益無改變。（答第二題）如果你睇過個地方，你會了解到，你講嘅問題（離開車廂踏上路軌）基本上係冇可能發生&hellip;車同月台之間嘅空隙非常細，人係冇可能跌或跳落去。<br />\n<br />\n李家超：喺月台跳落路軌就算發生，處理方法同處理非法入境者嘅方法無分別。<br />\n<br />\n問：如果有市民喺內地口岸區打交，觸犯刑事法例，送咗去香港醫院治理，之後會如何處理押解到內地審理的過程？<br />\n<br />\n李家超：如果有人未辦好入境手續但因為醫療問題進入香港，治療後就當作一般未有正常辦手續的入境者處理，入境處有一貫做法，如有需要會派員陪同辦理入境手續，若不應讓該人士入境，會將佢送離香港範圍。<br />\n<br />\n問：如果在西九龍站內地口岸區分娩，如何界定嬰兒身份？<br />\n<br />\n李家超：在內地口岸區出生的兒童，由於該區適用內地法律，所以會當是非香港出生。<br />\n<br />\n問：喺月台等車上唔上到Facebook？（英文問題）<br />\n<br />\n袁國強：我唔知呢條問題嘅答案&hellip;&hellip;這是一條好問題，我也想知道答案，謝謝你提出問題。<br />\n<br />\n問：李局長指內地人員在內地口岸區，日常巡邏會帶警棍，會否配槍？是否只在收到恐襲情報之下，才會配槍？<br />\n<br />\n李家超：內地口岸區由內地法律適用，運作方面必須尊重，其自主權是由內地相關單位決定其實際運作模式。我理解一般而言，廣東省口岸的運作模式，巡邏時是配備警棍。在甚麼情況之下他們需要添加裝備、哪一類裝備，一定要按實際情況，由當地機關決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E7%AB%99%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8Afacebook-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7-%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9F%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%258Afacebook-%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&d=6JTSrdTuKre8kJwcSCWYnhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c238c255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%258Afacebook-%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&h=50f499ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E5%9C%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E7%AB%99%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8Afacebook-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7-%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9F%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88/</a>"},{"pid":"f3fe208a4da8c4e9ec84aebf3c87d55901b65cfd","tid":335163,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"到時咪用黎走水貨  晒氣"},{"pid":"62f7f9dde6104ad0c49d92bcfeee8bd7de412062","tid":335163,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"炒撚咗佢啦"},{"pid":"05b533a1eac4c8c6c0673b3f470b4a5f06e683af","tid":335163,"uid":48083,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg&h=e3af6910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母擘大眼講大話</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1a0ee4da47d379b3a98f8bb60ffef93165fb55b8","tid":335163,"uid":131084,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"成件事無稽至極<br />\n都可以係香港發生<br />\n廿三條都好快打到黎"},{"pid":"a4530e0641e1a8ab0eaef8491d5605aa12957122","tid":335163,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"用BNO 入境  算唔算強一個保護？"},{"pid":"0053723b1a694f3551f284b451ffd30cf61eb3df","tid":335163,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"多"},{"pid":"e27ca316b3ea9872cb8ac4ff1987e1c7cbfd964c","tid":335163,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用BNO 入境  算唔算強一個保護？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先係中國人。"},{"pid":"a4af13b94d54084239642ef3a36f9e1c67461b1c","tid":335163,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8861f7fa107300f001ffae72b08883dd2d39d47b","tid":335163,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"BT呢？"},{"pid":"8bd99892e727a32fa59f1f53039e88c2b40bde83","tid":335163,"uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母強國猿都生CANCER<br />\n仲死性不改<br />\n一陣個天又收你呀"},{"pid":"85265b78926fe545114ee7212a7c55bec67cdcf9","tid":335163,"uid":84751,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"問：如果在西九龍站內地口岸區分娩，如何界定嬰兒身份？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">李家超：在內地口岸區出生的兒童，由於該區適用內地法律，所以會當是非香港出生。</span><br />\n<br />\n遲早又俾人告上終審, 終審又話佢地有香港身份, 之後又唔會釋法, 最後成班賤拿落黎生蟲"},{"pid":"975195677798b1de8c1ee9d6c3ff9197c7d88008","tid":335163,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg&h=e3af6910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母擘大眼講大話</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n其實如果不停括西九, 所謂地下終會變陸地. <br />\n所以話地下主權屬中國係荒謬. <br />\n<br />\n當然你話咩香港係中國擁有, 當你岩. 但係香港政府有土地範圍主權. 所以咩法律係中國人手上都係廢既, 佢玩中文字掩耳盜鈴根本就講晒."},{"pid":"7011e30caef8b900e426062eaeee055183025ba1","tid":335163,"uid":130001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"acddf7f14c963dc1e609553d66e42f28f5392b02","tid":335163,"uid":99964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:50:03.000Z","msg":"屌，睇到好撚嬲"},{"pid":"254f588414ea1a2fa643e014d7cd8c27802da5ac","tid":335163,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"有無咁on9"},{"pid":"3466710e6ba15afbd8b225d305f46b5077bb5882","tid":335163,"uid":38554,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"求其啦...唉 已經冇得救 我地都冇能力反對"},{"pid":"744210cb260e8d567df56773548157d93dcce6c0","tid":335163,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"好灰心"},{"pid":"b7a0943930fbaa78d3a996925b4673100684cc1f","tid":335163,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"無腦賣港"},{"pid":"2f2bac6e34416b42cf2fdf3e0f26721413f498fb","tid":335163,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg&h=e3af6910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母擘大眼講大話</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n其實如果不停括西九, 所謂地下終會變陸地. <br />\n所以話地下主權屬中國係荒謬. <br />\n<br />\n當然你話咩香港係中國擁有, 當你岩. 但係香港政府有土地範圍主權. 所以咩法律係中國人手上都係廢既, 佢玩中文字掩耳盜鈴根本就講晒.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公我贏，字你輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66b8ffc38f6168262d94a800ba0cfe382fe4741","tid":335163,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"睇到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c1002c3f62d7644881a0058dd1cccbea695f15","tid":335163,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"強國猿食撚屎"},{"pid":"e08b0a73051cd8bdbf2a0ae8302bf11a3bf812d9","tid":335163,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"發叔實等埋你"},{"pid":"71c32f33e6957047c2698eef66b60185863ffc55","tid":335163,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"1fc0443a583cf566a3acd651fb9e17005188814d","tid":335163,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:04:14.000Z","msg":"上個網有無犯法老答唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f348e7e32a23ad7d9642d0b4d6549c369f27c0f9","tid":335163,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人用高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedec0d29e8da39e20575eb08016a9368d765aa4","tid":335163,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇人用高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時班大媽公安捉你上車"},{"pid":"a33aa2f41fb157ca8fc7e68f1fb7