" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶成隊解放軍都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成架車運解手軍都得，有咩唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea58f4c9952cf9fe66c9e8a8d358276e354e75e4","tid":335163,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係蠢撚到仆街"},{"pid":"5c93b92dcf8c0f7d5163ec4044b63f6b0913f0ba","tid":335163,"uid":104065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"賣港賊真係越黎越痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個方案講香港去深圳一早已經有先例 但你係落馬洲過去起碼係過左條橋先俾內地check<br />\n講到好似完全無問題無所謂咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果通過左 遲下好快又會話咩港鐵係內地管轄範圍 要好似大陸咁俾人check袋 真係好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d5bdca3eb55b4d3fb90123da4e7c810d6387e0","tid":335163,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人用高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係比你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻豬，高鐵你覺得真係比香港人用咩？<br />\n高鐵同港豬澳都係俾支那解放軍攞嚟第日鎮壓我地嗰陣時用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d460c8d4ff8af457a3f1d029daa1ccfb7a4cd56","tid":335163,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母出賣香港<br />\n佢老豆死唔眼閉"},{"pid":"8cc45d0e73598e727b93e8ca494d894e9246f91b","tid":335163,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"好貼題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26acb3c84d39b88af4f8a33c184ed0c46323f669","tid":335163,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時咪用黎走水貨  晒氣</blockquote><br />\n痴線？一張高鐵飛肯定唔會平"},{"pid":"94c85d28cc7ef2315bf5663b224d6c6ae8ea7a2d","tid":335163,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個熱門得一個post講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟中央想香港點？<br />\n無理由會想香港死，但係點解會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港d官又係，咁做究竟有咩好</blockquote><br />\n咁做香港點死？唔好諗到反共，泛民，本土，連登就係香港先得嫁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋個個愛國愛港愛中央，根本唔驚咩俾公安拉入去捉上大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係知道九龍站附近D樓又準備升多嗰double，連帶全香港的樓又會升，香港人又發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cb95415cc9532a7f14d2c0dcc7851b9e4be1d4","tid":335163,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問：李局長指內地人員在內地口岸區，日常巡邏會帶警棍，會否配槍？是否只在收到恐襲情報之下，才會配槍？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">李家超：內地口岸區由內地法律適用，運作方面必須尊重，其自主權是由內地相關單位決定其實際運作模式。我理解一般而言，廣東省口岸的運作模式，巡邏時是配備警棍。在甚麼情況之下他們需要添加裝備、哪一類裝備，一定要按實際情況，由當地機關決定。</span><br />\n<br />\n即係帶火箭炮都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶成隊解放軍都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解放軍一向都駐守緊係香港，換防又好，調兵遣將入香港，其實都唔需要香港政府批准，呢個係中央的權力範圍。"},{"pid":"0d0d8215f05a42f1aefa2016d979a6f51590f6bd","tid":335163,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人用高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係比你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻豬，高鐵你覺得真係比香港人用咩？<br />\n高鐵同港豬澳都係俾支那解放軍攞嚟第日鎮壓我地嗰陣時用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家駐港解放軍全香港都有兵營，政府總部隔離已經有駐軍。廣州軍區十五分鐘內已經可以空降傘兵落中環。"},{"pid":"bfd184a01afd26a476c636f7d9325bf11dfeb5cf","tid":335163,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成個熱門得一個post講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟中央想香港點？<br />\n無理由會想香港死，但係點解會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港d官又係，咁做究竟有咩好</blockquote><br />\n咁做香港點死？唔好諗到反共，泛民，本土，連登就係香港先得嫁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋個個愛國愛港愛中央，根本唔驚咩俾公安拉入去捉上大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係知道九龍站附近D樓又準備升多嗰double，連帶全香港的樓又會升，香港人又發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知你好愛國<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/221447_b281d0ec19a4b59476dc8ffa4f449e06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F221447_b281d0ec19a4b59476dc8ffa4f449e06.jpg&h=b3aa7051&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/221453_aa20a69c01c156f0c0eae0144fa7967e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F221453_aa20a69c01c156f0c0eae0144fa7967e.jpg&h=e17b2898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2009f5889861976077fa176571bcdf71aa7355c5","tid":335163,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實有冇人用高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係比你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻豬，高鐵你覺得真係比香港人用咩？<br />\n高鐵同港豬澳都係俾支那解放軍攞嚟第日鎮壓我地嗰陣時用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家駐港解放軍全香港都有兵營，政府總部隔離已經有駐軍。廣州軍區十五分鐘內已經可以空降傘兵落中環。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好混淆視聽<br />\n解放軍都法律上都係受香港駐軍法等管制<br />\n依家係割地用支那法<br />\n兩樣野黎<br />\n同埋附近有老解同一地兩檢係咪違基本法無關<br />\n<br />\n吳靄儀兩分半鐘完整講解高鐵既法律問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/335112?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/335112?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7646fbc23182a432a7baaccd5800ee510d4de6db","tid":335163,"uid":41154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"坐洗頭鐵方便到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adad7825345476b1177c3bb1dc0083923c03e82b","tid":335163,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F191619_6b987101f0627822ea6bd32a29ccc16e.jpg&h=e3af6910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母擘大眼講大話</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母呢d小6常識已經有教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過依家唔知仲有冇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6bbad2df7e4250e12cc888b1fee7f5f11e64fd","tid":335163,"uid":1858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初頭得羅湖落馬洲兩關，起碼都算邊境區，依家一野直入香港中心地段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要割撚埋地比班狗用狗治方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好笑係得出左個問題，如果我老婆咁啱係個狗地盤／狗鐵上面生我，我地應否掉個仔個路軌，為佢好由佢死左去算。冇啦啦冇人變狗，冇陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0412a2b6919d88c31413c5c08fbdbd6969019","tid":335163,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初頭得羅湖落馬洲兩關，起碼都算邊境區，依家一野直入香港中心地段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要割撚埋地比班狗用狗治方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好笑係得出左個問題，如果我老婆咁啱係個狗地盤／狗鐵上面生仔，我地應否掉個仔個路軌，為佢好由佢死左去算。冇啦啦冇人變狗，冇陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"41d1bbdb9684968f72d47d7f5bcbe1ae21bb3e37","tid":335163,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母出賣香港<br />\n佢老豆死唔眼閉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef02f56f8f4f76f7cec89a787bfbd1cf865c8128","tid":335163,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eb29845eb1eb2e1b78fbc7b612713a8a2f9c36","tid":335163,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"有得移民就移啦<br />\n冇就做賤民啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">sorry中国人冇你份亦冇我份</span>"},{"pid":"545abe613c0eee0993027d21c3cd9f94168d5540","tid":335163,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf14f9967942e9c83480858698cc94afeaec2610","tid":335163,"uid":111506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"依家要入香港都要經香港海關。但係如果佢哋喺香港嘅範圍入面有管轄權，佢哋嗰啲執法人員入咗嚟香港都無人知，好快啲人都會被消失"},{"pid":"03fa39c36ce13eb7277693a6cfb58f03115527f3","tid":335163,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家要入香港都要經香港海關。但係如果佢哋喺香港嘅範圍入面有管轄權，佢哋嗰啲執法人員入咗嚟香港都無人知，好快啲人都會被消失</blockquote><br />\n就算無左個關<br />\n大陸都落黎香港捉人啦<br />\n其實見到香港哩家咁<br />\n真係好撚灰心"},{"pid":"8a78e95fa3ba9a79e623af575166f63c685ae1fc","tid":335163,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"香港比班賣港狗不斷出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa08d5b02963ba6a9b4978b5b93f50d2344e405a","tid":335163,"uid":22632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港比班賣港狗不斷出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班撚樣有權有錢 <br />\n第日中共接管哂香港<br />\n班撚樣個個拎住堆錢番外國嘆世界<br />\n我地就係到受苦，屌佢老母"},{"pid":"e603af21d34006ed306ec5ff643506654ec2b864","tid":335163,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530a745baa3ea22eea79d2b2d82f53585cfe1d5a","tid":335163,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8623a00f9c75d0aada9bbe025e2f382a16be6cee","tid":335163,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7763398a43fef23b43b115f449dbfb112355bec","tid":335163,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"我想問點解會唔知呢 你冇得話事架...依架在咩地方起野呀"},{"pid":"04bc4a273c7606fa589ea4a6fbadcfecebb50b0c","tid":335163,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明俾人架空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲死撐決定同支那政府無關<br />\n死撚咗佢啦強國猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d3c9ad39c704f2d1f77ce1bcdc754d0ceaef34","tid":335163,"uid":22362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問：如果在西九龍站內地口岸區分娩，如何界定嬰兒身份？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">李家超：在內地口岸區出生的兒童，由於該區適用內地法律，所以會當是非香港出生。</span><br />\n<br />\n遲早又俾人告上終審, 終審又話佢地有香港身份, 之後又唔會釋法, 最後成班賤拿落黎生蟲</blockquote><br />\n洗鬼咁生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早大撚把雙非啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f781c7985fccee732c8b83d5a0fcb2ea31faec5b","tid":335163,"uid":37584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"仆街陷家剷黎 死撚左佢算啦賣港賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d717b675ebe047c83ba49c6110ce90f18bc5885","tid":335163,"uid":102110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"跟本係香港地區犯法要受香港法律制裁。內地海關係西九只可管你可唔可以出入境。"},{"pid":"df1a00123cb0a883f08577496a1dfbd7e881607c","tid":335163,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟本係香港地區犯法要受香港法律制裁。內地海關係西九只可管你可唔可以出入境。</blockquote><br />\n正路應該係咁<br />\n但支那野心太大"},{"pid":"c52ca513c70ffcb8eaa3893f593a0ccb823a85b7","tid":335163,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"windows, apple 份 eula 話可以取用使用者 d 資料<br />\n港豬咪又係照用"},{"pid":"ad9324bf19db1a5d51be36fe43f69c30b56ec573","tid":335163,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟本係香港地區犯法要受香港法律制裁。內地海關係西九只可管你可唔可以出入境。</blockquote><br />\n正路應該係咁<br />\n但支那野心太大</blockquote><br />\n據聞原本港共係提議咁<br />\n但支那要求直情割地俾佢<br />\n之後港共當然配合支那既野心"},{"pid":"b9061751fda0d933ddd46066a8ed8c4912dd4a4e","tid":335163,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>跟本係香港地區犯法要受香港法律制裁。內地海關係西九只可管你可唔可以出入境。</blockquote><br />\n正路應該係咁<br />\n但支那野心太大</blockquote><br />\n據聞原本港共係提議咁<br />\n但支那要求直情割地俾佢<br />\n之後港共當然配合支那既野心</blockquote><br />\n仲要扮到成功爭取保留業權果下真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ca3949814e94f29d814b2dda39abf0ebc47cbf","tid":335163,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20