啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個記者問錯哂。<br />\n應該問佢&ldquo;如果有內地孕婦係站內穿羊水，應如何處理？如最後在港醫院分娩，如何定義嬰兒的身份？&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n以佢講法話就算有人跳落路軌都係當非法入境處理<br />\n有人受傷入醫院都當未入境論<br />\n應該係唔算香港BB</blockquote><br />\n出生同入境係兩件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64a7346436420bc0075a37c13c206cde70dc01f","tid":335163,"uid":53206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:46:30.000Z","msg":"食屎啦正一冚街產死仆街<br />\n強國猿你而家係咪當我地成班死蠢白痴乜都唔識<br />\n格硬行一地兩檢又話咩符合一國兩制<br />\n你咁中意中共果套就自己切碌鳩出黎獻俾雜種吧啦"},{"pid":"333eb9ea28e19bf7a01762fd2ec7cd80960e5e91","tid":335163,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T18:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時咪用黎走水貨  晒氣</blockquote><br />\n高鐵票價應該好貴下，水貨佬應該唔會用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75337980e2c8e8cffb1041bf92f9cda3a28ab267","tid":335163,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到時咪用黎走水貨  晒氣</blockquote><br />\n高鐵票價應該好貴下，水貨佬應該唔會用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下走咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走粉走iPhone就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8756abc430dec5ea0c316433985d629fe2b86c5","tid":335163,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}